40:52.075 --> 40:56.454
you know you look at me
and see someone I am not.

40:56.454 --> 40:58.623
A government minister's
daughter,

40:58.623 --> 41:01.584
this person to revere
and admire, but...

41:01.584 --> 41:04.087
I'm not the daughter
of a minister.

41:04.087 --> 41:07.298
I am the daughter of a woman

41:07.298 --> 41:09.592
who lost everything

41:09.592 --> 41:12.470
and is now deranged and cruel,

41:12.470 --> 41:15.390
and maybe one day,
I gonna be just like she.

41:15.390 --> 41:19.018
And I accept my fate.
- No, don't say that.

41:19.018 --> 41:20.478
Don't say that.

41:20.478 --> 41:22.689
You are smart and beautiful,
and you deserve the world,

41:22.689 --> 41:24.982
and I am gonna give it to you.

41:24.982 --> 41:28.778
Clive,

41:28.778 --> 41:32.240
