41:32.240 --> 41:34.992
You never have.

41:34.992 --> 41:39.205
And I don't know what might be
missing in your life

41:39.205 --> 41:44.293
that I represent, but...

41:44.293 --> 41:47.964
what you feel for me
is not true.

41:47.964 --> 41:51.926
You wrong.

41:51.926 --> 41:54.470
I do know you.

41:54.470 --> 41:56.931
And I do love you.

41:56.931 --> 41:58.474
If Edwin hadn't got in the way,

41:58.474 --> 42:00.977
you would've realized
you loved me too.

42:00.977 --> 42:03.020
Clive. Clive.

42:17.368 --> 42:18.870
I went to the gift shop
with Mom

42:18.870 --> 42:22.206
