three whole days off

42:28.337 --> 42:30.757
before I have to go to school,
which means

42:30.757 --> 42:33.968
we can even do it twice
if you want.

42:33.968 --> 42:35.845
But you promised.

42:35.845 --> 42:38.931
Claire, you can eat candy
and watch a movie by yourself.

42:38.931 --> 42:40.892
Okay?

42:40.892 --> 42:43.686
I promise you,
you will get over this.

42:43.686 --> 42:45.396
Okay?

42:45.396 --> 42:47.565
I love you. Bye.

42:57.158 --> 43:01.162
I mean, um, we got
to do this.

43:01.162 --> 43:04.165
I thought she was hanging out
with her sister tonight.

43:04.165 --> 43:05.166
Bitch.

43:13.800 --> 43:15.635
Mm, I hope you're ready, Goges.

43:15.635 --> 43:18.262
Tonight we will lime
like it's 1999.

43:18.262 --> 43:19.722
You know what I'm...

43:19.722 --> 43:25.186
I know
what you did... to Sara.

43:25.186 --> 43:27.313
Hey, boys.

43:27.313 --> 43:28.689
I'm excited.

43:30.900 --> 43:32.443
Hi.

43:32.443 --> 43:36.155
How far away is Paulette's?

43:36.155 --> 43:38.366
Is this okay to wear?

43:38.366 --> 43:40.409
You look--

43:40.409 --> 43:43.371
you look just fine, Alison.

43:43.371 --> 43:44.413
Thanks.

43:45.957 --> 43:48.084
Nice ride.

43:48.084 --> 43:49.502
Oh, thank you very much.

43:51.838 --> 43:54.590
Come on.
Let's go.

