to everyone we know.

44:20.950 --> 44:22.368
No one's heard from her.

44:22.368 --> 44:24.162
You, anything?
Nothing.

44:24.162 --> 44:26.122
I went to the waterfront.
I checked Clive's apartment,

44:26.122 --> 44:29.208
